rComments: I really enjoyed this course. Prof Fianu clearly cares about her students and their success in class, and makes an effort to learn everyone's name. Lectures are interesting, and the assignments and exams are not too hard as long as you attend class and keep up with the reading. Assignment guidelines are always very clear. 100% would take again.
She's a great prof that cares about her students and truly tries to help them succeed. She was always available outside of class to answer any questions. Would recommend if you're a FI student
Amazing prof. If you are looking for someone who is caring and interested in what she is teaching, I would definitely recommend her. Her classes are not easy but they are 100% worth it.

Même s'ils ont beaucoup de matière, les cours de la professeure Fianu sont toujours très bien préparés. Ses travaux sont exigeants mais pas impossibles. Elle est toujours disponible pour aider ses étudiants et offre la possibilité de faire des travaux pour des notes bonus. Elle prend aussi le temps d'apprendre le prénom de ses élèves!

She's a great professor. She offered us a chance to earn bonus marks, although the assignments/tests were not hard so it didn't matter much in the end. Lectures are encompassing and well structured, not particularly inspired but still interesting. Really nice person and very approachable. Would recommend this prof.

If you're looking for a bird-class you might want to avoid her, but if you're looking for a fantastic professor and an interesting class go for it! She expects her students to work hard, but she's there to help. Her readings are important and class is mandatory. If you're passionate about medieval studies I highly recommend taking this class!
Elle s'attend à ce que ses étudiants travaillent fort, mais elle est excellente professeure.

Prof is a very tough marker. If you don't partake in the weekly discussions and miss a single weekly 'submit a definition of a new word' assignment, YOU WILL FOREVER BE IN HER BAD BOOKS. DO NOT TAKE THIS CLASS UNLESS YOU'RE WILLING TO PUT IN A LOT OF WORK
Assignment instructions are so vague. Very hard marker, but is understanding and allows make-up assignment. Nice prof but i'd avoid her in the future.
Best teacher ever! She really wants to help her students and her classes are always very interresting.
Very interesting!! Really knows her stuff super well. Very helpful also. But she is a very hard marker. Go see her if you are not sure what to do with your projects she gives guidelines.

Prof. Fianu is very clear at explaining the subject matter and is patient and helpful if you have questions (don't be shy to go to office hours!). The work may seem easy but you definitely have to put time and effort into it.
My favourite prof ever! Unlike other profs, she can actually teach very well, is extremely helpful and super interesting. Make sure you take good quality notes, and your good to go!
Unnecessarily difficult. Nice person and she obviously knows what she's talking about, but bad at explaining it. Doesn't even have notes and gives mixed messages on assignment.

Horrible prof, horrible class. I had an A average and she nearly failed me then told me based on her own bias that i wasn't smart enough  to study history in her opinion.  Avoid this harpy at all costs.

One of the best history teacher i've ever had. She's easy to follow, clear, and funny. The only problem is the correction. The exams/homework themselves seem easy, but she's very hars on the correction.
Had her 12 years ago for a 2nd year course and a 4th year seminar (La ville au Moyen Age). She's one of the best. She asks a lot from her students (she pushes them hard) but gives them a lot as well.
Awwwww her accent IS so cute!!! But for real she's a good prof - knows her stuff, and makes her expectations more or less clear. Would reccommend her.
bonne prof, mais donne beaucoup de travail
Knows what she is talking about and manages to keep the content interesting for the most part. Very demanding, don't expect to get by in her class without putting in an effort.

Fabulous! She is passionate about the subject matter. She is approachable and helpful. She does not treat you like student number and legitimately wants to further your learning experience in the classroom. She is very relaxed and encourages discussion. I would take any class by her, she made the subject matter interesting and easy to understand.

Don't know the exact code for this course so made it up. It was a second year but I also took a 3rd year with this prof. Ok, class is NOT mandatory but I highly recommend it. The textbook use is heavy but she makes it easier to understand. Granted, she does have an accent (during da meeedle aaaages) but it's actually pretty cute. She has a baby fac
Ok teacher I guess.
a very knowledable lady.  Always helpful.  One of my favouirite profs.  Although she gives a lot of work, she is very fair in her marking.  Very funny if you get to know her.

Great class : I finaly understood what was the medieval period. pr fianu is very helpful and has a true commitment to MA's. The class was hard but I had the chance to meet her and to improve a lot in my writing as well as in my researchs... Thanks prof Fianu, thanks to you I know where i'm going.
Très sevère
Nice woman, very knowledgable. However, English is not her first language so some things are a little confusing.
Hard marker, bit of a harda*s... Nice lady.
Very interesting. Above all, she knows what she's taking about.
No Comments
